data.description: Welcome to your perfect starter family home! This charming single-family 3 bed, 1 bath home is waiting for you. 1 year old tankless water heater. Washer and dryer in garage. Located in a quiet neighborhood. Enjoy the convenience of being located within minutes of local grocery stores and many delicious restaurants. Additionally, this home is just a stone's throw away from the new Sunseeker resort on the harbor. If you love to fish, this is the perfect town for you with the harbor nearby and many great local seafood restaurants. It's time to make this your own and enjoy all that this wonderful home and town have to offer!    Roof was damaged form the hurricane and is outdated so it will need a new one. I have attached an estimate for a new shingle roof and another estimate for a new metal roof. There is ceiling water damage in the back lanai area where the flat roof is.
